普鲁士多特蒙德的主教练[[尤尔根·克洛普|尤尔根·克洛普]]评论称，漫长的赛季让多特蒙德疲于应对。他表示，“在经历了一个艰难的赛季后，比赛已经很迟了，从第75分钟开始我们就非常艰难，但我们应该进入决赛，今晚我们证明了这一点”。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/may/25/champions-league-final-quotes|title=Borussia Dortmund's Jürgen Klopp rues Bayern Munich's late winner|date=2013-05-25|work=Guardian UK|accessdate=2013-06-11|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107070858/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/may/25/champions-league-final-quotes|dead-url=no}}</ref>多特蒙德的后卫[[马茨·胡梅尔斯|马茨·胡梅尔斯]]说，这场比赛非常接近也实在令人失望，他们在前25分钟表现不错，但错失了所需的进球。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/competitions/champions-league/10080988/Borussia-Dortmund-1-Bayern-Munich-2-match-report.html|title=Borussia Dortmund 1 Bayern Munich 2: match report|date=2013-05-26|work=Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2013-06-11|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107070905/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/competitions/champions-league/10080988/Borussia-Dortmund-1-Bayern-Munich-2-match-report.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>拜仁主教练[[尤普·海因克斯|尤普·海因克斯]]则表示“我们取得了一些特殊的成就”。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/may/26/bayern-munich-jupp-heynckes-borussia-dortmund|title=Bayern Munich's Jupp Heynckes: 'We have achieved something unique'|date=2013-05-25|work=Guardian UK|accessdate=2013-06-11|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107070907/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2013/may/26/bayern-munich-jupp-heynckes-borussia-dortmund|dead-url=no}}</ref>

